{"title":"CSS —— 效果","date":"2019-11-25T02:29:56.224Z","thumbnail":"https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/11/25/MXOUNd.md.jpg","link":"2019/11/25/CSS-effect","tags":["CSS","面试"],"categories":["Programming"],"updated":"2019-12-24T02:22:53.430Z","content":"<h2 id=\"box-shadow\">box-shadow<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-effect#box-shadow\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight css\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* x偏移量 | y偏移量 | 阴影模糊半径 | 阴影扩散半径 | 阴影颜色 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">box-shadow</span>: 2<span class=\"selector-tag\">px</span> 2<span class=\"selector-tag\">px</span> 2<span class=\"selector-tag\">px</span> 1<span class=\"selector-tag\">px</span> <span class=\"selector-tag\">rgba</span>(0, 0, 0, 0<span class=\"selector-class\">.2</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* 插页(阴影向内) | x偏移量 | y偏移量 | 阴影颜色 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">box-shadow</span>: <span class=\"selector-tag\">inset</span> 5<span class=\"selector-tag\">em</span> 1<span class=\"selector-tag\">em</span> <span class=\"selector-tag\">gold</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>作用：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>营造层次性（立体感）</li>\n<li>充当没有宽度的边框</li>\n<li>特殊效果</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"text-shadow\">text-shadow<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-effect#text-shadow\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight css\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* x偏移量 | y偏移量 | 模糊半径 | 颜色 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">text-shadow</span>: 1<span class=\"selector-tag\">px</span> 1<span class=\"selector-tag\">px</span> 2<span class=\"selector-tag\">px</span> <span class=\"selector-tag\">black</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>作用：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>立体感</li>\n<li>印刷品质感</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"border-radius\">border-radius<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-effect#border-radius\"></a></h2><ul>\n<li><p>圆角矩形</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>圆形</p>\n<p>border-radius: 50%以上</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>半圆/扇形</p>\n<p>border-top-left-radius: 100px，其余为0，可以制作扇形。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>一些奇怪的角</p>\n<p>border-radius: 10px 10px 10px 10px/20px 20px 20px 20px;</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"background\">background<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-effect#background\"></a></h2><ul>\n<li><p>纹理、图案</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>渐变</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>雪碧图动画</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>背景图尺寸适应</p>\n<p>background-size: cover(保持长宽比覆盖容器) | contain (保持长宽比且保持图片完整)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"clip-path\">clip-path<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-effect#clip-path\"></a></h2><p>对容器进行裁剪</p>\n<ul>\n<li>常见几何图形</li>\n<li>自定义路径</li>\n<li>clip-path: circle(50px at 100px 100px)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"transfrom\">transfrom<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-effect#transfrom\"></a></h2><p>对元素进行变换</p>\n<ul>\n<li>translate(位移)</li>\n<li>scale(缩放)</li>\n<li>skew(斜切)</li>\n<li>rotate(旋转)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"面试题\">面试题<a href=\"2019/11/25/CSS-effect#面试题\"></a></h2><ol>\n<li><p>如何用一个div画xxx</p>\n<ul>\n<li>box-shadow无限投影</li>\n<li>::before</li>\n<li>::after</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>如何产生不占空间的边框</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>box-shadow</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>outline</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>如何实现圆形头像</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>如何实现iOS图标的圆角</p>\n<p>clip-path:(svg)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>如何实现半圆、扇形等图形</p>\n<p>border-radius</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>如何实现背景图居中显示/不重复/改变大小</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>如何平移/放大一个元素</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>如何实现3D效果</p>\n<ul>\n<li>perspective: 500px;</li>\n<li>transform-style: perserve-3d;</li>\n<li>transform: translate rotate…</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","prev":{"title":"CSS —— 动画","link":"2019/11/25/CSS-animation"},"next":{"title":"CSS —— 布局","link":"2019/11/23/CSS-layout"},"plink":"http://allenxz.github.io/2019/11/25/CSS-effect/","toc":[{"title":"box-shadow","id":"box-shadow","index":"1"},{"title":"text-shadow","id":"text-shadow","index":"2"},{"title":"border-radius","id":"border-radius","index":"3"},{"title":"background","id":"background","index":"4"},{"title":"clip-path","id":"clip-path","index":"5"},{"title":"transfrom","id":"transfrom","index":"6"},{"title":"面试题","id":"面试题","index":"7"}]}